{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I caught one contract issue before mirroring it to the frontend: the first backend draft would have put `schema_version` inside every nested `extracted_values` object, which would make model output unnecessarily noisy. I\u2019m fixing that no...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_47", "text": "I caught one contract issue before mirroring it to the frontend: the first backend draft would have put `schema_version` inside every nested `extracted_values` object, which would make model output unnecessarily noisy. I\u2019m fixing that now so the shared contract stays clean and easier for the parser to emit.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 92, "prompt_index": 31, "prompt_name": "30 \u2014 Chat-to-UI Action Schema", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T04:30:41-07:00"}
